===Noun phrase===
'''[[phase]] [[transition]]'''

#{{physics}} The [[transition]] between [[thermodynamic]] [[phases]] of a [[physical system]], especially one between the [[solid]], [[liquid]], and [[gaseous]] phases of a substance.

